ّةٌ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "A company of men going a gentle pace:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Msb:) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "daAf~apN", "text_ar": "دَافَّةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[alone]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a party journeying together not a hard pace:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AA, T:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "an army going gently,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "leisurely, towards the enemy:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, K: *)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a company of men coming from one country"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "town to another:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(IDrd, M:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a party going to a great town"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "city:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a company of men journeying leisurely"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "("}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "yadif~uwna", "text_ar": "يَدِفُّونَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ")"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "in search of herbage and sustenance:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(Z, TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a party of the people of the desert journeying to a region of green herbage and waters in consequence of drought:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and [hence]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "a party having rain after experiencing drought;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "as also ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "daf~aAfapN", "text_ar": "دَفَّافَةٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ". (M.) See 1, in two places."}], "source_refs": ["M", "T", "Msb", "AA", "IDrd", "TA", "Z"]}]}, "classical_definitions": {"source": "hawramani", "url": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/%D8%AF%D8%A7%D9%81/", "headword_ar": "دأف", "entries": [{"lexicon_id": "dictionary_1", "lexicon_en": "Ibn Manẓūr, Lisān al-ʿArab (d. 1311 CE)", "lexicon_ar": "لسان العرب لابن منظور", "permalink": "https://arabiclexicon.hawramani.com/?p=2336#19f0e4", "body_html": "<p>دأف: دَأَفَ على الأَسِيرِ: أَجْهَزَ. ومَوْتٌ دُؤافٌ: وحِيٌّ.</p><p>والأُدافُ: ذكر الرجل، قال ابن الأَعرابي: أَصله وُدافٌ من قولهم وَدَفَ الشَّحْم</p><p>إذا سالَ، وإن صحَّ ذلك، فهو من غير هذا الباب.</p>"}]}, "translations_attribution": {"model": "qwen36-35b-heretic", "generated_date": "2026-05-18", "pipeline_version": "words.translation.v1.spark"}}